data.title: Raquel Torres ( Mexican screen actress ) and Stephen Ames ( former husband of Adrienne Ames ) were married aboard the liner Lurline in Los Angeles harbour
data.meta_description:
Raquel Torres ( Mexican screen actress ) and Stephen Ames ( former husband of Adrienne Ames ) were married aboard the liner Lurline in Los Angeles harbour - after the ceremony the couple sailed aboard the same ship for a honeymoon in Honolulu - photo shows Raquel Torres and Stephen Ames after their wedding 

May 2nd 1934
